data.description: Looking for the non-cookie cutter home in a mature tree-lined neighborhood? This is it! Fantastic 3 bedroom 2 bath home in SE Decatur. Large family room with built-in's and cozy fireplace. Hardwood floors in main areas, extra great room with many possibilities. New water heater. Crawlspace encapsulation done 2020. HVAC 4 years old. Extra large driveway. Large fenced-in back yard great for entertaining. Minutes to Point Mallard, I-565, I-65 and Huntsville.
